master

Delay TP main figures

This is a master script for the main figures in R.

# load intertemporal choice trial data
load('~/repos/delaytp/data/all_trials_naivetp.RData')
# load follow-up and new group fits and data
load('~/repos/delaytp/data/delaytp.RData')
# load raw tpdata
timing <- read.csv(file = "~/repos/delaytp/data/timing_trials.csv")
tetp = subset(timing,te == 1)
tptp = subset(timing,te == 0)
# load R-squared for individual fits
load('~/repos/delaytp/data/real_r2.RData')
# load fitted draws for example subject
load('~/repos/Human_TimePercepetion/Analysis/data/dfsubj.RData')
# load new posterior
load('~/repos/delaytp/data/new_posterior.RData')
